criteria.exclusion_criteria:
(1) received hormonal therapy in the latest 3 months;
(2) cannot endure pregnancy due to severe body diseases;
(3) accompanied with severe mental diseases, acute urogenital system inflammation, sexually transmitted disease;
(4) with hereditary disease that are not allowed to have baby; drug abuser or having harmful addiction; in touch with radiation, toxin, drug within action period that could cause malformation.
The patients participating in this trial had to withdraw all the other Chinese herbal decoctions and Chinese patent medicines.
